condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :LA Sch 2, Sec I.C, para 12(b) and (c); and PA Schedule, Sec I.B, para 1 | Description :Establishment of theindependent Project Grievance Redress System | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :LA Sch 2, Sec I.C, para 4(a) & (c); and PA Schedule, Sec I.B para 3(a) & (c) | Description :Confirmation ofreadiness of the Confined Disposal Facility (CDF), and continued operations and supervision of the CDF throughout projectimplementation | Frequency :Quarterly

Finance Agreement :LA Sch 2, Sec I.C, para 6; and PA Schedule Sec I.B, para 5 | Description :Testing of Sections of the ProjectSite prior to the dredging of the Section, to determine presence of Hazardous Material. Conditions for the handling of HazardousMaterial, if any are found by the tests. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :LA Sch 2, Sec I.D para 5(a) & (b); and PA, Schedule, Sec I.C, para 2 | Description :Preparation andimplementation of Environmental Safeguards Documents for each project site. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :LA Sch 2, Sec I.D, para 16(d) & 17(d); and PA Schedule, Sec I.C para 7(d) & 8(d) | Description :Preparation andimplementation of Resettlement Plan for each project site with Project Affected Persons (PAPs) | Frequency :CONTINUOUS
Finance Agreement :LA Sec 5.01 | Description :Conditions for Effectiveness | Due Date :17-May-2012
